about.description: ogs5py: a python API for OpenGeoSys5
about.summary: ogs5py: a python API for OpenGeoSys5

name: ogs5py
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "ogs5py" %}
{% set version = "1.0.5" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: dfde1763dd033ebeef380d098ffb8af47e8f72dead477bb6c9eeceeb342f9358

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - setuptools
  run:
    - lxml
    - meshio
    - numpy >=1.13.0
    - pandas >=0.23.0
    - pexpect
    - python
    - vtk
    - whichcraft

test:
  imports:
    - ogs5py

about:
  home: "https://github.com/GeoStat-Framework/ogs5py"
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "ogs5py: a python API for OpenGeoSys5"
  description: "ogs5py: a python API for OpenGeoSys5"
  doc_url: https://geostat-framework.readthedocs.io/projects/ogs5py/
  dev_url: https://github.com/GeoStat-Framework/ogs5py

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - MuellerSeb
